---

<Layout 
  title="Anix Lynch — AI Data Engineer & Architect | Portfolio"
  description="Explore the portfolio of Anix Lynch - AI Data Engineer specializing in machine learning, data visualization, and cloud solutions. Projects in AWS, GCP, Azure, and Snowflake."
  image="/profile-photo.jpg"
>
  <Sidebar {...portfolioData.personal} />
  
  <main class="main">
    <PageNav showBack={false} />
    
    <!-- Ops Stack Section -->
    <section style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
      <h2 style="font-size:1.75rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:1rem;color:#333;">🔬 Production Ops Stack</h2>
      <p style="color:#666;margin-bottom:2rem;line-height:1.6;">How I monitor 13 production AI systems: agent traces, data quality gates, lineage tracking, and cost monitoring</p>
      <div class="projects">
        {portfolioData.opsStack.map(dashboard => (
          <ProjectCard {...dashboard} />
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Bullet 1: Multi-Cloud -->
    <section style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
      <h2 style="font-size:1.75rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:1rem;color:#5BA3C5;">🌐 Multi-Cloud Infrastructure</h2>
      <p style="color:#666;margin-bottom:2rem;line-height:1.6;">Built pipelines on AWS, Azure, and GCP. Everything's Terraform-managed and runs serverless for ~$1-2/month.</p>
      <div class="projects">
        {portfolioData.projects.filter(p => 
          p.title.includes("AWS Data Engineering") ||
          p.title.includes("Cocktailverse") ||
          p.title.includes("Network Intelligence")
        ).map(project => (
          <ProjectCard {...project} />
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Bullet 2: AI-DE Multi-Pain -->
    <section style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
      <h2 style="font-size:1.75rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:1rem;color:#4FB3C8;">🎯 AI-DE Multi-Pain</h2>
      <p style="color:#666;margin-bottom:2rem;line-height:1.6;">The messy stuff: point-in-time correctness, training-serving parity, streaming ETL, data quality gates. Hit 98.8% AUC, 149ms p95, went from 12 incidents/month → 0.</p>
      <div class="projects">
        {portfolioData.projects.filter(p => 
          p.title.includes("Churn ML") || 
          p.title.includes("Fraud Detection") ||
          p.title.includes("Coffeeverse")
        ).map(project => (
          <ProjectCard {...project} />
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Bullet 3: GenAI Multi-Pain -->
    <section style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
      <h2 style="font-size:1.75rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:1rem;color:#5DC1D8;">🤖 GenAI Multi-Pain</h2>
      <p style="color:#666;margin-bottom:2rem;line-height:1.6;">Built agents that don't break at 3 AM. RAG pipelines, 14-tool orchestration, 93% task success, ~1% hallucination. Runs serverless for $1-2/month.</p>
      <div class="projects">
        {portfolioData.projects.filter(p => 
          p.title.includes("AI Agent Job") || 
          p.title.includes("Mocktailverse") ||
          p.title.includes("AI Business Intelligence") ||
          p.title.includes("Multimodal GenAI")
        ).map(project => (
          <ProjectCard {...project} />
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Bullet 4: Domain Translation -->
    <section style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
      <h2 style="font-size:1.75rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:1rem;color:#A8C5D9;">💼 Domain Expertise</h2>
      <p style="color:#666;margin-bottom:2rem;line-height:1.6;">Ex-VC/PE → AI builder. Built production tools for legal (VC term sheets), finance (cap table modeling), marketing (campaign analytics), and enterprise BI. Business context = better code.</p>
